br />\n大叫我係支那狗都得"},{"pid":"32b4aae7cce58c144f4fdfa6cd301517bfa4f9ba","tid":2401291,"uid":34872,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:25:04.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 但我預左番唔到香港<br />\n巴打 冇特區 講出黎 好多人都會笑鳩你 點解唔續 咁唔方便果d傻西說話<br />\n另外 而家走入中國大使館搞特區護照 同中國主動登記自己係Bno 真係講唔過去<br />\n而家情況未係咁惡劣 咪博下用身份證番去 但再出黎果陣 你未必用到Bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真 如果香港人唔係咁鐘意食兩家茶禮 有著數先去續Bno <br />\nBno 命運未必會咁撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c185d568489f5ea107eb549c696a7c770e1c58","tid":2401291,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:27:33.000Z","msg":"咁都要問，唔好返黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95fed101dafb0c0761bfa296558ad107d71c15b","tid":2401291,"uid":194298,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1631126cc6f16f26a153bcb6be79c70b769e1d9f","tid":2401291,"uid":71997,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"quote":{"pid":"27415333666356a3b9bf147fad042a82cdc69996","tid":2401291,"uid":79302,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"唔係出示either Passport or HKID咋咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"你好似冇比錢買過機票咁喎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n訂機票要填passport, 航空公司已被通知唔收BNO, 放你佢地好撚麻煩，點解要幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:28:27.000Z","msg":"你好似無比錢買過機票咁<br />\n好多航空公司都唔駛填passport no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0155694f04818457e2665596a7487f12fd0abb8","tid":2401291,"uid":382422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02