人啦...<br />\n你有香港身分證就得...<br />\nBNO上面都有寫明你有香港居留權..."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:32:12.000Z","msg":"一年去幾次日本既香港人都知日本地勤一直都係會睇BNO+身份證黎證明有居留權<br />\n身份證就係居留證明，PASSPORT就係日本國承認既旅遊證件，今時今日都無改變<br />\n佢話佢長居日本竟然唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好低質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"即使無身分證<br />\n行入中國使領館claim自己係香港人<br />\n佢都會verify 你身分之後<br />\n issue emergency travel document 俾你<br />\n再唔係就打1868<br />\n入境事務處協助在外香港居民24小時熱線<br />\n<br />\n你有香港居留權嘅身份<br />\n唔會因為你手上面揸咩證件<br />\n或者有or無某啲證件而失去咗<br />\n即使你乜都無係手"},{"pid":"1d3b892240f696d1dc1673c73a6617f12f7776ee","tid":2401291,"uid":214679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:41:08.000Z","msg":"樓主講到成個日本得返JAL先有飛機飛嚟香港咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cathaypacific.com/cx/zh_TW/prepare-trip/travel-advisories/travelling-on-bno-passports.html?cxsource=nc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cathaypacific.com%2Fcx%2Fzh_TW%2Fprepare-trip%2Ftravel-advisories%2Ftravelling-on-bno-passports.html%3Fcxsource%3Dnc&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQuDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=3e53b23c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cathaypacific.com/cx/zh_TW/prepare-trip/travel-advisories/travelling-on-bno-passports.html?cxsource=nc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bGjkzfT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbGjkzfT.jpg&h=561dedf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d433f10f30781c9375bbc3187602f0df3bdc8d19","tid":2401291,"uid":57675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"277f2aab288def4eb4b9609470d40cfe7e016520","tid":2401291,"uid":117318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48ce68a9e0f562e3ac31accaf6422e15ff488f","tid":2401291,"uid":169741,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"(1) 歸化做日本人。羅日本passport番香港。<br />\n(2) 等平權派BC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:36:00.000Z","msg":"攞日本passport就要放棄BNO喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:45:05.000Z","msg":"我就覺得拎到日本passport仲好過BNO<br />\n利申 兩樣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b56f3bd3241343421fbc8a37c4aa55f3fe61046","tid":2401291,"uid":117318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d433f10f30781c9375bbc3187602f0df3bdc8d19","tid":2401291,"uid":57675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"277f2aab288def4eb4b9609470d40cfe7e016520","tid":2401291,"uid":117318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c48ce68a9e0f562e3ac31accaf6422e15ff488f","tid":2401291,"uid":169741,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"(1) 歸化做日本人。羅日本passport番香港。<br />\n(2) 等平權派BC<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:36:00.000Z","msg":"攞日本passport就要放棄BNO喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:45:05.000Z","msg":"我就覺得拎到日本passport仲好過BNO<br />\n利申 兩樣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:48:45.000Z","msg":"BNO有英國去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，雖然未必個個啱"},{"pid":"658687c8297955fdbd81bcdc0def186bb4ad45ff","tid":2401291,"uid":45858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d70b8891f63d775f9d8b0f6213bab18107e309bf","tid":2401291,"uid":147651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"喺日本到長住，入境同簽證全部都係用BNO<br />\n冇續廁所板好耐<br />\n我係咪一世都唔使返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕嘅嗰係出入境<br />\n香境入境用身分證，日本出境用BNO都冇問題<br />\n而家最大嘅難關係，搭飛機時check passport嗰關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個日本同事以前喺JAL做地勤，<br />\n佢話上機時check passport係為左check你有冇<br />\n入境目的地嘅權利（例如居住權/簽證）<br />\n<br />\n即是，就算JAL肯認我本BNO係有效旅行證件<br />\n目的地嘅香港唔認，佢都唔可以放我上機<br />\n<br />\n話就話可以喺駐日大使館到續廁所板<br />\n但咁就等於送羊入虎口同大使館講我係持BNO入日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然冇乜事都唔會返香港，<br />\n但係第日間唔中都想返下屋企見下阿媽<br />\n有冇熟地勤嘅巴絲有計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"日本地勤check 香港身份證就ok"},{"pid":"dd0a812abefbfcb618dbe23db957a7e4adba87b3","tid":2401291,"uid":267647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:23:21.000Z","msg":"身分證夠做"},{"pid":"d2fcdff6f5ebe7021f67a6c34fd1687969e271da","tid":2401291,"uid":147651,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"f82079c2cd140c80a7e86f07638d1768a893cd87","tid":2401291,"uid":194298,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"c0155694f04818457e2665596a7487f12fd0abb8","tid":2401291,"uid":382422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:28:48.000Z","msg":"唔好亂開post嚇人啦...<br />\n你有香港身分證就得...<br />\nBNO上面都有寫明你有香港居留權..."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:32:12.000Z","msg":"一年去幾次日本既香港人都知日本地勤一直都係會睇BNO+身份證黎證明有居留權<br />\n身份證就係居留證明，PASSPORT就係日本國承認既旅遊證件，今時今日都無改變<br />\n佢話佢長居日本竟然唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好低質"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"係啦唔夠巴打去得日本多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBNO+身分證可以上到機<br />\n但係目的地行政機關有權拎到抵港航班上旅客資料<br />\n咪又即係自爆自己拎bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心求問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=