h 但唔敢認自己係 British?"},{"pid":"75a517ade6decbc60256eaba19c85c82da75037a","tid":2401291,"uid":3093,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d2fcdff6f5ebe7021f67a6c34fd1687969e271da","tid":2401291,"uid":147651,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"f82079c2cd140c80a7e86f07638d1768a893cd87","tid":2401291,"uid":194298,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"c0155694f04818457e2665596a7487f12fd0abb8","tid":2401291,"uid":382422,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:28:48.000Z","msg":"唔好亂開post嚇人啦...<br />\n你有香港身分證就得...<br />\nBNO上面都有寫明你有香港居留權..."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T22:32:12.000Z","msg":"一年去幾次日本既香港人都知日本地勤一直都係會睇BNO+身份證黎證明有居留權<br />\n身份證就係居留證明，PASSPORT就係日本國承認既旅遊證件，今時今日都無改變<br />\n佢話佢長居日本竟然唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好低質"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:26:12.000Z","msg":"係啦唔夠巴打去得日本多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBNO+身分證可以上到機<br />\n但係目的地行政機關有權拎到抵港航班上旅客資料<br />\n咪又即係自爆自己拎bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心求問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"咁你究竟係擔心bno買唔到機票返香港<br />\n定係煩惱緊點樣向政府隱瞞你有bno?<br />\n雖然兩者都係庸人自擾"},{"pid":"4bc08772d0a71c7f4d870c540225d96f5129464e","tid":2401291,"uid":387907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T23:41:52.000Z","msg":"我去過好多次日本都係渣BNO<br />\ncheck in 都無畀人問身份證喎<br />\n國泰、港航、快運、全日空都搭過<br />\n<br />\n本身BNO上面observation有段字話你有right of adobe in HK<br />\n(我見過有朋友渣特衰畀人問身份證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n真係唔得咪攞張身份證畀地勤睇囉<br />\n<br />\n人哋都係打份工確保你入到境啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國去香港本身都免簽證啦<br />\n地勤鬼識咁多嘢咩"},{"pid":"810569c106fb1fe53d9b88d0f7b69681f34e0bd8","tid":2401291,"uid":128600,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"485e73b2f03de2825e67ae300